Mobile is the main device people use to find most of the products and services they consume online, and so, in most of the cases,
the mobile design should be prioritized. But, [Is Developing an app worth the cost?](http://mashable.com/2011/02/24/mobile-app-dev-cost/)
Not always: firstly because apps are much more expensive and takes longer to develop than web sites. Additionally, apps cannot reflect 
immediate changes because users have to download a new version to see the update. 
